title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Holden Colorado RC & Isuzu D-MAX 3.0L Diesel (2008-2011) Fuel Manager Pre Filter Water Separator Kit FM611DPK

content.rendered:
Finally we have a vehicle specific Fuel Filter / Water Separator Kit for:
2008-2011 Holden Colorado RC & Isuzu D-MAX 3.0L Turbo Diesels !
This Filter unit is to be used as a Pre Filter to separate water thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality.

This kit includes very detailed fitting instructions and everything you will need & even where to fit it !

Kit FM611DPK Contents :
• 1x Fuel Filtration Unit Fuel Manager
Made by Stanadyne in the USA !
(Filters down to 30 Microns !)
• Mounting Bolts, washers & Nyloc nuts
• Hand Primer Kit
• 6mm Bracket Mounting Bolt
• Spare 30 Micron Filter Element
• 7 Mtrs of 8mm Quality Fuel Hose
• Specially Designed Filter Bracket
• Brass male Quick fit fittings
• 90 Degree Female Quick fit fittings.
• 2x Blanking Plugs
• Hose Clamps
• Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)

Download PDF Info >

Install all fittings and plugs with the thread paste.
